                    <p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;">
    <li>Utility of imaging procedures in pretreatment staging of colorectal cancer </li>
    <li>Sensitivity, specificity, and accuracy of imaging procedures in pretreatment staging of colorectal cancer </li>
    <li>Detection rates for liver metastases </li>
    <li>Recurrence rates </li>
    <li>Overall survival </li>
</ul></p>

